parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night.
symptoms: The left headlight is not working
requiring the use of high beams to have adequate lighting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door actuator can cause the door to become stuck, trapping occupants inside, which is a safety hazard in emergency situations.
symptoms: The passenger-side door will not unlock with the vehicle in park
requiring the use of the center dash-mounted unlock button to open the door; the door will not open with a double pull on the door handle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the blower fan can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The blower fan runs on high and then shuts down
when the MAX/AC fan is turned on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An engine oil leak can cause the engine to seize or fail, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: warning display indicating drive train malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Cooling system failure can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage or failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Powertrain malfunction can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Warning display indicating drive train malfunction

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Driver's Side Door Lock Actuator Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's side door lock actuator can trap the driver inside the vehicle, creating a safety risk and potential emergency situation.
symptoms: The driver's side door will not unlock using the inside door handle
the door lock is jammed into the locked position
the door cannot be unlocked manually
the door can only be unlocked using the electric door unlock system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The reflection of the dashboard speaker and head-up display on the windshield can obstruct the driver's field of view, creating a hazardous driving condition and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The reflection of the dashboard speaker and head-up display covers more than 60% of the driver's field of view
creating a distracting and unsafe driving environment.
